Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:59.37,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}青く澄んだ　空は昨日と同じ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:04.59,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}はずなのに　少し不安で
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.57,0:19:11.04,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}いつものように　笑えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:17.30,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あの花のように　咲けるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.43,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}うつむきそうな今日を　照らしてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.43,0:19:31.74,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}出逢い　運命が動き出したの　微笑みの魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.74,0:19:38.88,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}愛で満ちてく　勇気と共{\fsp4}に{\fsp0}My heart
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:43.78,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あなたがくれた　この奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:52.22,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}前を向けたよ　きらめきはどこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.22,0:19:57.84,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}のびてゆく光
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:13.51,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}強く吹いた　風は明日に向かって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.51,0:20:18.87,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}置いてかれてしまいそうな　気がした
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.87,0:20:24.31,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}涙で濡れた頬を　拭ってくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.31,0:20:34.54,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}触れた　指先が熱く残るの　ときめきの魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:53.09,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}いつものように　笑えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.09,0:20:59.65,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あの花のように　咲ける{\fsp4}よ{\fsp0}My Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:07.70,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}愛で満ちてく　勇気と共{\fsp4}に{\fsp0}My heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.72,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}あなたがそばに　いるからね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.72,0:21:20.93,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}前に進むよ　きらめきはどこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.93,0:21:27.68,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}のびてゆけ光
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.47,0:18:59.37,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}清澈的天空 如同往日一樣
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.37,0:19:04.59,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}卻感到了些許不安
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.57,0:19:11.04,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果一如既往地歡笑
Dialogue: 1,0:19:11.04,0:19:17.30,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}能夠像那朵花一樣綻放嗎
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.30,0:19:22.43,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}悲觀的時光 得以照亮
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.43,0:19:31.74,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}相遇轉動了命運的齒輪 微笑的魔法
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.74,0:19:38.88,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}愛和勇氣充滿了我的心
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.88,0:19:43.78,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你給予我的這份奇蹟
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.78,0:19:52.22,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}讓我能夠昂首向前 光輝無限擴張
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.22,0:19:57.84,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不斷前進的光芒
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.42,0:20:13.51,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}風兒向著明天猛烈地吹著
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.51,0:20:18.87,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}感覺自己要被拋在原地
Dialogue: 1,0:20:18.87,0:20:24.31,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你抹去了我臉上的淚水
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.31,0:20:34.54,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}指尖的熱量留在了心間 心動的魔法
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.51,0:20:53.09,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果一如既往地歡笑
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.09,0:20:59.65,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就能夠像那朵花一樣綻放 我的夢
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.78,0:21:07.70,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}愛和勇氣充滿了我的心
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.70,0:21:12.72,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}因為你陪伴在我身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.72,0:21:20.93,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}我會昂首向前的 光輝無限擴張
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.93,0:21:27.68,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}前進吧 光芒
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「LOVE or HATE?」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.66,0:22:25.01,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば髪をちょっとなびかせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.41,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聴こえる声{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.99,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　何と言われても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.79,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}足は止めませんから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:39.06,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}飛ぶ鳥落とす勢い　ニュース
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:41.93,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}明日には忘れている
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.62,0:22:45.71,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}昨日よりも今日がいいよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.49,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}思い込み　大勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.56,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}リズムに合わせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.95,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}揺れていたいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.45,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}外野がうるさい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:02.31,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}ノイズ・キャンセリング
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:06.26,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}たとえば指をちょっとなぞらせたら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.68,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君のチョイス{\fsp4}は{\fsp0}LOVE or HATE？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.12,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}お好きにどうぞ　頬を赤くして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.31,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}唾を吐きかけ{\fsp4}る{\fsp0}Boy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.31,0:23:20.02,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}趣味の違い　安心の相違が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.90,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}君を戸惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.90,0:23:26.42,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}私の道　形作るのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.92,IN_JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}これだけ　Just LOVE or HATE
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.66,0:22:25.01,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是撩一下頭髮
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.01,0:22:28.41,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}聽到的會是喜歡還是討厭？
Dialogue: 1,0:22:28.41,0:22:31.99,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隨便吧 無論別人怎麼說
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.99,0:22:35.79,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}反正不會停下腳步
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.79,0:22:39.06,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}新聞的傳播勢不可擋
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.06,0:22:41.93,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}到了明天就忘了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.62,0:22:45.71,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}所以今天比昨天好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.71,0:22:48.49,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}精神勝利大法好
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.07,0:22:52.56,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}本想跟著節奏
Dialogue: 1,0:22:52.56,0:22:55.95,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}搖擺搖擺
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.95,0:22:59.45,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但外面也太吵了
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.45,0:23:02.31,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}噪音·消除
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.85,0:23:06.26,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}要是用手指轉個圈圈
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.26,0:23:09.68,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}你的選擇是喜歡還是討厭？
Dialogue: 1,0:23:09.68,0:23:13.12,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}隨便吧 憋紅了臉
Dialogue: 1,0:23:13.12,0:23:16.31,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}準備唾棄的男孩
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.31,0:23:20.02,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}興趣的不同 信仰的不一
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.02,0:23:22.90,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}讓你感到迷茫
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.90,0:23:26.42,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}但決定我前行方向的
Dialogue: 1,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.92,IN_CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}僅僅是喜歡還是討厭
